                <h1>How to Remove Wallpaper from Your iPhone: A Step-by-Step Guide</h1>
                <p>To remove wallpaper from your iPhone, open the Settings app, tap on "Wallpaper," then select "Choose a New Wallpaper." You can choose from Apple's collection or your own photos. To delete a wallpaper, simply set a new one to replace it. Finally, return to the Home screen to see your fresh look!</p>
